{
  "stem": "11272.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were playing together soccer all the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were so close before that it wasn't even funny.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But because his background was Schwabisch, he immediately joined the Hitler Youth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he became an SS man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he became an Obersturmfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the horrible part I remember is that he became the worst Jew-hater and the worst Nazi that ever lived.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Unfortunately, I found out that after the war, the Russians captured him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they hanged him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he was absolutely, unbelievably horrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He, he, he made monkeys out of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He made all kinds of nasty remarks, and-- not directly at me, at other Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yeah, one time after an incident, he and I slept on top of a haystack.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in the summer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I asked him, Jonczi, how could you do that?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're my best friend.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, I love you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you're a Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Hitler says that the [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Jews are our misfortune.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we've got to dispose of you people so that Germany will become the 1,000-year Reich, because we will control the world for a thousand years.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because that's what he was taught in the Hitler Youth, that the Jews are the only ones that are in their way to take over the world.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, a lot of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most, most of them-- they did some horrible things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They, they not only ignored us, but they made sure that we can't buy food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Food was rationed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Jews didn't get coupons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some of the neighbors from other villages used to come past our shop and trade with dad for, for work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they turned those people in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it, it was-- it was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
